  "footnotes": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "text": "You must follow these requirements if you entered MIT in Fall 2025 or later."
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "text": "Includes subjects as of Fall 2026"
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "text": "Each completed subject can only be used to satisfy at most one _required_ subject but can be used to satisfy multiple _additional constraints_."
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "text": "![](https://eecsis.mit.edu/images/fall.gif): only offered fall term ![](https://eecsis.mit.edu/images/spring.gif): only offered spring term grey: not offered this academic year."
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "text": "If you choose a Math requirement as an elective, it must not have [essentially similar content](https://math.mit.edu/academics/undergrad/major/#similar) to the other subjects satisfying your 6-4 degree requirements."
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "text": "At least _two_ of your completed subjects must be on the [CIM2](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#CIM2) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [AI+D\\_SERC](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#AI+D_SERC) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [Data-centric](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#Data-centric) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [Model-centric](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#Model-centric) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [Decision-centric](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#Decision-centric) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [Computation-centric](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#Computation-centric) list"
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "text": "At least _one_ of your completed subjects must be on the [Human-centric](https://eecsis.mit.edu/degree_requirements.pcgi?program=6-4#Human-centric) list"
    }
  ],
